  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Psychological stress is an independent cardiovascular risk factor. Activation of platelets
      plays an important role in atherosclerosis development and it could one of the mechanisms
      linking psychological stress and cardiovascular diseases
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
